{"tid":1391821,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求法律解答 搶口罩算唔算意圖永久地剝奪他人財產","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T22:11:34.000Z","uid":42691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd66aba51903541626ca690002d2d570d1be3b96","tid":1391821,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">根據香港法例第210章《盜竊罪條例》盜竊罪的基本定義：「如任何人不誠實地挪佔屬於另一人的財產，意圖永久地剝奪該另一人的財產，即屬犯盜竊罪。」 \n\n「永久奪去他人的財物」則指某人取得財物時，即使未有意永久取得該物件，但仍毫無顧忌地把財物當成自己的，且不顧物主的權利，也會當是「永久奪去他人的財物」看待。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n網上好似好多片喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法律巴絲快d解答 冇理由咁都冇罪既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【橙‧識法】擅取東西後歸還是否算偷竊？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2018/01/26/010081865.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ftopic%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F010081865.shtml&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=5fa6414f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/topic/system/2018/01/26/010081865.shtml</a></span>"},{"pid":"42b0785a49b0a089495e0a4901f34e548ba9144a","tid":1391821,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef8d03f8a6a2bca168c3502f68667cce44f05475","tid":1391821,"uid":209198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42b0785a49b0a089495e0a4901f34e548ba9144a","tid":1391821,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"用你id覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc45ba772f8b09ade28e2e53442976fa39d53cf","tid":1391821,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:37:57.00